text: Janat Ansari () is a Nepalese politician. He is a member of Provincial Assembly of Madhesh Province from People's Socialist Party, Nepal. Ansari, a resident of Birgunj, was elected via 2017 Provincial Assembly of Madhesh Province election from Parsa 1(A). ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Nepalese politicians
title: Janat Ansari
